# Privacy Policy

## 1. Introduction

**PoliShadow** is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our Discord bot.

## 2. Information Collection

- **Data You Provide**: When you interact with PoliShadow, you may provide information such as your Discord username and user ID.

- **Automatically Collected Data**: We may collect data related to your interactions with PoliShadow, including commands issued and server information, to provide and improve our services.

## 3. Use of Information

We use the collected information to:

- Provide and maintain PoliShadow services.
- Monitor and analyze usage to improve functionality.
- Respond to user inquiries and support requests.

## 4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

PoliShadow does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties except as described below:

- **Service Providers**: We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our bot.

- **Legal Requirements**: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.

## 5. Data Security

We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

## 6. Your Choices

- **Access and Update**: You can access and update your personal information by managing your Discord account settings.

- **Deletion**: You can request the deletion of your data by contacting us at [your-email@example.com](mailto:your-email@example.com).

## 7. Changes to Privacy Policy

PoliShadow reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

## 8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [FallingPlanetCorp@gmail.com](mailto:FallingPlanet@gmail.com).
